Class RateLimitException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • sx.blah.discord.util.RateLimitException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RateLimitException
extends Exception
    Represents a 429 TOO MANY REQUESTS return code from a url connection. This happens if your bot exceeds a Discord api rate limit.
